claim.t.sol
├── when the campaign has expired
│  └── it should revert
└── when the campaign has not expired
   ├── when the recipient has already claimed
   │  └── it should revert
   └── when the recipient has not claimed
      ├── when the index is invalid
      │  └── it should revert
      └── when the index is valid
         ├── when the recipient address is invalid
         │  └── it should revert
         └── when the recipient address is valid
            ├── when the amount is invalid
            │  └── it should revert
            └── when the recipient address is valid
               ├── when the merkle proof is invalid
               │  └── it should revert
               └── when the merkle proof is valid
                  ├── it should mark the index as claimed
                  ├── it should create an airstream
                  └── it should emit a {Claim} event
